article_headline: The Aggies put an abrupt stop to the Mustangs’ drive towards a
article_text: Saturday when they soundly defeated the Mustangs, 5-2. Matches between the two teams are always huge because year after year the teams butt heads in the nationals. Saturday’s match was the rubber match of this season. The Aggies beat the Mustangs, 5-4, the first matchup. The Mustangs more than made up for the first loss by thrashing the Aggies, 8-1, in the Mustang Invitational.
